      "writtenOn": "2026-03-10T05:44:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "After thinking more about it, I agree with your suggestion.\n\nIn practice each PCIeDevice exposes a single Function0, and extracting the trailing digits from the path filename (Function0 → 0) is sufficient. \n\nI\u0027ll switch to getAssociatedSubTreePaths and drop the pendingCount approach.",
      "parentUuid": "7554c956_3613d0e9",
      "revId": "21c91b05c30181329bf9fe994676248393a2f554",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
